name: Hypnotic Mandalas | Abundance
description: First one out of series of kaleidoscopic Sacred Geometry Mandalas. This animated loop is based on the Mandala of Abundance. It helps you to attract abundance in all it's forms: money, ideas, opportunities, experiences... Clear your mind and get lost in the endless transformation. Original design & animation: Yulia Babanova. 3000x3000, animated loop, mp4.
